# Ultrasonic Oxygen sensor
# Stm32f0
# Oled 2.4 inch for showing purity , flow and temprature of the oxygen 
# smd buzzer with pwm 
# Battery base
# 4 page menu designed for setting limits and alarms
# Optimized power and micro memory consumption
# ADC , INTERRUPT , TIMERS , SPI ,UART
# Industrial device manufactured in the Iranian market
